natspec.author: Curve.Fi
natspec.details: This contract is only a template, pool-specific constants must be set prior to compiling

add_liquidity(uint256[4],uint256).notice: Wrap underlying coins and deposit them in the pool

params._amounts: List of amounts of underlying coins to deposit
params._min_mint_amount: Minimum amount of LP tokens to mint from the deposit

returns._0: Amount of LP tokens received by depositing

calc_token_amount(uint256[4],bool).details: This calculation accounts for slippage, but not fees. Needed to prevent front-running, not for precise calculations!
calc_token_amount(uint256[4],bool).notice: Calculate addition or reduction in token supply from a deposit or withdrawal

params._amounts: Amount of each underlying coin being deposited
params._is_deposit: set True for deposits, False for withdrawals

returns._0: Expected amount of LP tokens received

calc_withdraw_one_coin(uint256,int128).notice: Calculate the amount received when withdrawing and unwrapping a single coin

params._token_amount: Amount of LP tokens to burn in the withdrawal
params.i: Index value of the underlying coin to withdraw

remove_liquidity(uint256,uint256[4]).details: Withdrawal amounts are based on current deposit ratios
remove_liquidity(uint256,uint256[4]).notice: Withdraw and unwrap coins from the pool

params._amount: Quantity of LP tokens to burn in the withdrawal
params._min_amounts: Minimum amounts of underlying coins to receive

returns._0: List of amounts of underlying coins that were withdrawn

remove_liquidity_imbalance(uint256[4],ui.notice: Withdraw coins from the pool in an imbalanced amount

params._amounts: List of amounts of underlying coins to withdraw
params._max_burn_amount: Maximum amount of LP token to burn in the withdrawal

returns._0: Actual amount of the LP token burned in the withdrawal

remove_liquidity_one_coin(uint256,int128.notice: Withdraw and unwrap a single coin from the pool

params._min_amount: Minimum amount of underlying coin to receive
params._token_amount: Amount of LP tokens to burn in the withdrawal
params.i: Index value of the coin to withdraw
